Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: James Mason remembered, 1984
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf0x
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Aug 1984
Remembering James Mason, the character actor who wouldn't play the Hollywood game. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.